me":"七深","body":"欸嘿嘿，能被這麼說真是太高興了。\n而且我們也玩得非常開心","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile06","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"像是Fes上的美食跟拍照布景之類的，\n都有種青春的感覺……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"idle01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"還有訊息板也很棒喔。\n傍晚時Monica的大家有一起去寫呢～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"idle01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"嗯、嗯，我有讀大家的訊息喔！\n覺得真的好有大家的風格，讓我忍不住露出笑容了呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"對吧～。尤其是小透的\n『捲起Monica旋風吧！！！』\n廣町我也很喜歡喔～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"idle01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"呵呵，小透的訊息就算沒寫名字，\n也一看就知道是誰寫的呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"還有小唯也寫了訊息對吧。\n真讓人開心呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"其實啊，讓人意外的是，\n唯唯是最先寫完的人喔。最後寫的人是小白～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"idle01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"原來是這樣啊。\n小真白寫的我記得是～……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"是『跟Popipa一起辦2MAN LIVE！』喔","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"對對！\n因為小真白最喜歡Popipa了嘛","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"是啊。正因為他真的超喜歡Popipa，\n所以也有些讓人驚訝的地方……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nod01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev289-me2-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"跟Popipa辦2MAN LIVE，我覺得這對小白來說，\n不是能夠那麼輕易寫出來的事。\n應該需要很大的勇氣吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"thinking01","expr